title: Miles Davis "Time After Time" Live 2CD
description:
This is a live recording  of the 1989 version of the Miles Electric Group. Sound quality is great for a live small label recording. The versions of the songs have lots of extened solo sections and plenty of stretching. (Check out Kenny Garrett and the band as they build the tag ending groove of Human Nature until it explodes)
Source CD
Jazz Door Records 1993 
MP3 files 192kb made with iTunes. 

Tracks: 
CD1 
1.Jilli
2.Hannibal 
3.Intruder
4.Star People  
5.Perfect Way 
6.Mr Pastorius 
7.Human Nature

CD2
1.Tutu
2.Time After Time
3.Full Nelson
4.Me and You 
5.Carnival Time
Vienna Friday November 5 1971 

Miles w/Kenny Garrett, Kei Akagi, John Beasly, Foley, BEnny Rietveld, Ricky Wellman, Monyungo Jackson
